{"tid":1834140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港首確診】新年和你SHOP防疫版！和你CLEAN！","createTime":"2020-01-22T09:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T03:52:00.000Z","uid":70786,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"052c94ffae447968369565c9ac7826ae749c4968","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"鄧小強話嚟緊過年，市民都想出街同去拜年<br />\n<br />\n文匯報都出篇文<br />\n店前「和你咳」嚇客 藉肺炎煽恐慌<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1833805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1833805</a><br />\n<br />\n原來咁多人唔知新年有任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家香港有第一宗武漢肺炎確診<br />\n和你咳係好危險<br />\n有見及此，想建議大家搞個防疫版和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和你clean</strong></span></span><br />\n核心成員裝備&mdash;&mdash;董太裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1400000/1403659/biln20030413009_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1400000%2F1403659%2Fbiln20030413009_630_1024.jpg&h=a61c3c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/files/timelinephoto/169/photo/1520873250-0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2Ffiles%2Ftimelinephoto%2F169%2Fphoto%2F1520873250-0.jpg&h=3abe0ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係叫你真係著到成個董太咁，自己上去Amazon搵hazmat suit<br />\n買滿$49美元免運，順便同d口罩運返嚟香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本款有白色，另外仲有黃金戰衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61maVIQ801L._UX342_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61maVIQ801L._UX342_.jpg&h=5702178b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加埋防毒面罩同手套就可以開工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清潔工具：<br />\n1:99或1:49稀釋家用漂白水<br />\n毛巾同噴壺<br />\n漂白水使用方法可以參考政府網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/tc/useofbleach.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fsars%2Ftc%2Fuseofbleach.htm&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=cf72f464\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/tc/useofbleach.htm</a><br />\n路人所需裝備：平就外科口罩或貴少少N95(1860/1860S/1870/1870S)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動方針：<br />\n去商場／藍店外幫手清潔，噴下抹下咁，視乎人流加減頻率，最基本每半小時一次<br />\n少人去咪唔使清潔得咁密囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扶手／門柄／Lift掣要加緊清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有保安問你或者被截查，就同佢地講你係幫世衛做防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為世界衛生站在最前線犯法呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人趕就去出入口做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果鄉黑曱甴王又玩濫捕而俾傳媒影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報紙條題就會係 香港警察打壓志願防疫工作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個仆街政府根本冇心冇魄力去做好防疫工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地唔搞就由我地市民自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦想係度點名屌鳩陳肇始條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港已經有確診個案，一定要困埋佢入隔離病房<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要佢用護士身份親手照顧支那肺炎病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗最多幫佢立個像，紙紮果隻燒翻俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c2504ea61566e816b4bf9d022c18d36eefad09","tid":1834140,"uid":274435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"收到風用火殺菌有用<br />\n我懷疑狗屋多病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99ea67e503f353096ff7eccc1ef63dc8a88720c","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"和你咳好危險呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推到多D人睇到"},{"pid":"457f4f28b55dfc33c45edfefffea1ed1f6b0dc6d","tid":1834140,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413b3e325e38db509fc7a8a81a4da629eed2ab49","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"行動POST冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共放個肺炎落嚟就成功搞散個運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登快D發賀電恭喜林鄭成功旨暴制亂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105e1eaca4ea5762e339f6bc47918249be0b4350","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪一個確診個案<br />\nd勇武就匿返去屋企唔光復香港喇"},{"pid":"8057b0876c219cc9692b031ea03775645c29452c","tid":1834140,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"和你shop 限時特別版<br />\n<br />\n完全唔洗靠人多<br />\n<br />\n3~4個董太裝入藍店已經夠嚇走全部客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗渣刀渣槍 董太裝行街唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80098dc131b4e4f0002051f4c9f31988bc0be18","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8057b0876c219cc9692b031ea03775645c29452c","tid":1834140,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"和你shop 限時特別版<br />\n<br />\n完全唔洗靠人多<br />\n<br />\n3~4個董太裝入藍店已經夠嚇走全部客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗渣刀渣槍 董太裝行街唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"唔係要嚇走人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要保護到自己同防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183910a1e57565314555d45144c5f795de7330ec","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"千載難逢機會<br />\n如果俾狗亂咬<br />\n仲可以狂咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6472b86fc75406296569ff394258502f290a61","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"有確診都唔推po唔做野<br />\n香港人等入度假村啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53327454a091afe13bfb2cd3b91a358f33869f5a","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"巴絲幫手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人推唔郁呀"},{"pid":"27d83225233b0c6abf701b353d2a24d9e78ca33d","tid":1834140,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:17:47.000Z","msg"