.jpg\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32c235985eaedceec77b97c878693327049b48b","tid":1834140,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"和你clean"},{"pid":"feaebf57a4ed69f08e5bb699611dc4126ffdd85e","tid":1834140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"成班港豬都仲未知共產黨想點玩<br />\n政府堅持就禁蒙面法違憲上訴<br />\n只識出廣告叫人同暴力割蓆，但唔叫人洗手戴口罩<br />\n林鄭一出trip香港就爆第一宗確診<br />\nPK鄧指示下屬要截查戴口罩後生仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}